  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\nCase 1: **The button 'Save' is not shown while editing a category**\r\n1. Create a new community with 3 channels and one category with one channel\r\n2. Go to change the category, select a few channels, and check the button 'Save'\r\nActual Result:\r\nThere is no Save button\r\n<img width=\"398\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/214755217-411561fe-4907-4df6-b84e-08c498752e57.png\">\r\n\r\n**Case 2: The 'Save' button is overlapped by the 'Delete category' area while editing a category**\r\nSteps:\r\n1. Create a new community with 3 channels and one category with one channel\r\n2. Go to change the category, select a few channels, and hover over the 'Delete Category' area\r\nActual Result: The 'Save' button is overlapped by the 'Delete category' area while editing a category\r\n<img width=\"356\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/214755727-76d85d04-8984-4b14-a8dd-7e84f9e6c003.png\">\r\n\r\n**Case 3: The 'Edit category' looks incorrect if there are some channels and the empty Category title**\r\n<img width=\"252\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/214755963-9ac2540f-b0d4-4ffb-bdf6-9b20a89befe1.png\">\r\n\r\n**Case 4: The grey line disappears if channels are scrolled**\r\n1. Create a new community with  four channels and go to create a new category,\r\n2. Enter a space in the Category Name field\r\n<img width=\"249\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/214756583-fd4f1237-5583-458a-aae7-58bc090c272b.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe modal looks correct\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: master\r\n- Operating System: macOS Monterey\r\n\r\n",
